{"tid":1421321,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝咁多位手足 差d忍唔撚住喊出黎","createTime":"2019-08-06T07:44:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T07:57:26.000Z","uid":176858,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a9b53e2010c4e2c64934d2f4afc76472a89b5eb6","tid":1421321,"uid":176858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:44:32.000Z","msg":"之前有參與過多次遊行都系普通集會<br />\n但尋日發夢 係我第一次落手落腳幫大家手<br />\n發夢發左好耐 體力都消耗得七七八八又無晒糧水<br />\n我一路幫大家手 我問d手足有無水 <br />\n佢比左盒m&amp;m同支茶我 個刻好感動<br />\n之後我繼續幫唔同既手足 <br />\n我一邊做野一邊有人遞水比我飲<br />\n又有其他手足叫我抖下 話我幫左好耐<br />\n有一刻我好感動好想喊 但我忍住左<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知自己講乜撚野 <br />\n但我覺得香港人真係好撚團結<br />\n大家素未謀面 可以互助互愛<br />\n希望有一日可以同大家除低面罩相認<br />\n<br />\n個盒m&amp;m係我成世人食過最撚好食既m&amp;m<br />\n個支茶係我成世人飲過最撚好飲既茶<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TG0oNvp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTG0oNvp.png&h=aee52795&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n亦都多謝一路遞水比我飲既手足<br />\n支水特撚別解渴特撚別好飲<br />\n我唔會忘記大家"},{"pid":"7efb505425e9aeb54429fcabb32563e6d3d661b4","tid":1421321,"uid":253833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:45:41.000Z","msg":"香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f06dbb79e30e06e224a227b4ad1a8349fb2aed","tid":1421321,"uid":253833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:45:51.000Z","msg":"和理非新回合<br />\n［借acc][純建議] 8月24日 全港罷買日 搞「靜」香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1420749\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1420749</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dd2cf83f716d43b8e683f92629533ca31961bade","tid":1421321,"uid":41327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:47:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港係我哋屋企，大家屋企人仲計較咁多？"},{"pid":"2aacf0993af8833c